<b>Attacks:</b><br>
During attack points are calculated which are +10% or -10% of the actual number.
Approximately 250 points kill 1 enemy soldier. Thus, if you are attacking you would need
about 16 archers to kill 1 soldier, but the defense needs only about 8.5 archers
to kill one of your soldiers.<br>
If you keep attacking the same person than your gains will get smaller and smaller.<br>
Whoever has more points wins the battle.
<br>
<br>
Army Attacks - use swordsman, archers, horseman, macemen and trained peasants.<br>
Conquer - wins land<br>
Raid - destroyes resources and buildings of attacked empire<br>
Rob - steals resources from attacked empire<br>
Slaughter - kills populations<br>
<br>
Catapult Attacks - use catapuls<br>
Catapult Army and Towers - when won, some of enemy's army and towers are destroyed<br>
Catapult Population - kills enemy people<br>
Catapult Buildings - destroys buildings<br>
<br>
Thief Attacks - use thieves<br>
Steal Information - find out how much army and resources your enemy has<br>
Steal Research Info - find out research information of your enemy<br>
Steal Building Info - find out how many of each building your enemy has<br>
Steal Goods - steal resources from enemy<br>
Poision Water - kills some of enemys army and population<br>
Set Fire - destroys some of enemy's buildings
