<b>Trade</b>
<br>

You can use the Local Trade to trade between your people. It's good
to use it at the beginning of the game, because as you get bigger 
selling prices go down and buying prices go up.
<br>
You can use auto trade feaure to have good traded automatically each turn.
<br>
When selling or buying on public market the transaction is beeing done between
other empires. It takes 3 turns to send your goods to the public market. After the
goods are bought you get the cash right away, but there is 5% transaction fee.
Once your goods arrive at the market you can withdrawal them at any time, but 10%
of your goods will be takes as a restocking fee.
<br>
When you buy goods from the public market it takes 3 turns for them to arrive.
<br>
