<b>Research</b><br>
You can research different areas to improve your empire growth or your military power.<br>
The more levels of research you have, the more research points are needed to research next level.<br>
The following researches are available:<br>
* military<br>
1. attack points - each level increases your attacking power by 1%<br>
2. defense points - each level increases your defense power by 1%<br>
3. thief effectivness - your thief steal/burn/poison effectivness is increased by 1%<br>
4. military loss - each level makes your military losses during battles decrease by 1% (this research is limited to 50 levels)<br>
<br>
* production
5. food production - hunters and farms produce 1% more food<br>
6. mine production - gold mines and iron mines produce 1% more gold and iron<br>
7. weapons and tools production - your weaponsmiths and tool makers produce 1% more goods<br>
<br>
* other<br>
8. space effectivness - your warehouse space is increased by 1% and house space is increased by 1%<br>
9. markets - you can sell/aid 1% more goods <br>
10. explore - explorers find 1% more land<br>
