<b>Starting Tips:</b>
<br>
Here are some tips at getting started with the game.<br>
At the beginning do not worry about building big army, you can gain way more land from
exploring than fighting. Make sure you have always some room for your people to grow,
build houses when needed and make sure your food ratios are high enough for your people to grow fast.
<br>
Also collect enough food to send maxiumum number of explorers, because it will cost
you more food to send then next time. <br>
Build tool makers to make your buildings build faster. Once you have enough tools
shut down tool maker production to around 20% save iron, wood and gold.<br>
Build town centers to increase number of explorers you can send.<br>
At the beginning it's hard to get a lot of cash from gold mines because mountains are hard to get.
So build food production or wood production and sell at local market. Use the auto trade feature.
